int which softens at 60 degrees.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><b style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\">How long does Squishy Plastik stay </b><b><u>mould-able</u></b><b style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\">?</b></span>\r\n\r\nSquishy Plastik stays mould-able for up to 2 minutes before hardening and can be reheated continuously to continue shaping.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>What can Squishy Plastik be used for?</strong></span>\r\n\r\nSquishy Plastik has 1000\'s of uses from home application to creative ideas. For example:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>D.I.Y</li>\r\n 	<li>Fixing</li>\r\n 	<li>Prototyping</li>\r\n 	<li>Jewellery</li>\r\n 	<li>Toys</li>\r\n 	<li>Moulds</li>\r\n 	<li>Science</li>\r\n 	<li>STEM</li>\r\n 	<li>Medical</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe only limit is your imagination!','What is Squishy Plastik?','','inherit','closed','closed','','4-revision-v1','','','2018-01-24 07:14:54','2018-01-24 07:14:54','',4,'http://homepages.shu.ac.uk/~b6031184/selfix_technology/uncategorised/4-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(311,2,'2018-01-24 07:15:15','2018-01-24 07:15:15','[foogallery id=\"75\"]','Uses','','inherit','closed','closed','','9-revision-v1','','','2018-01-24 07:15:15','2018-01-24 07:15:15','',9,'http://homepages.shu.ac.uk/~b6031184/selfix_technology/uncategorised/9-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(312,2,'2018-01-24 07:15:49','2018-01-24 07:15:49','','Our Shop','','inherit','closed','closed','','11-revision-v1','','','2018-01-24 07:15:49','2018-01-24 07:15:49','',11,'http://homepages.shu.ac.uk/~b6031184/selfix_technology/uncategorised/11-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(313,2,'2018-01-24 07:16:05','2018-01-24 07:16:05','[wpforms id=\"39\"]','Contact Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','13-revision-v1','','','2018-01-24 07:16:05','2018-01-24 07:16:05','',13,'http://homepages.shu.ac.uk/~b6031184/selfix_technology/uncategorised/13-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(314,2,'2018-01-24 07:30:31','2018-01-24 07:30:31